"**Odoo-alusta:** Kaikki Odoo-alustat ovat tuettuja, mukaan lukien Odoo "
"Online, Odoo.sh ja On-Premise-asennukset."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/online_food_delivery.rst:57
msgid ""
"**Delivery platform reseller account:** A registered reseller account is "
"required with each delivery platform to be integrated (e.g., Uber Eats, "
"DoorDash, Careem, Deliveroo, Zomato)."
msgstr ""
"**Toimitusalustan jälleenmyyjätili:** Rekisteröity jälleenmyyjätili "
"vaaditaan kullekin integroitavalle toimitusalustalle (esim. Uber Eats, "
"DoorDash, Careem, Deliveroo, Zomato)."

