msgstr "Raportointisivun elementit"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:26
msgid ""
"All subscriptions-based reporting pages can be accessed via "
"the :guilabel:`Reporting` header menu in the **Subscriptions** app."
